Titolo: Frame Gride

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Frame Gride (フレームグライド, Furēmu Guraido) is a Japanese mecha fighting game made for Dreamcast by FromSoftware in 1999.
Similar to From's Armored Core series, the mecha in the game are heavily customizable.The game had a single-player mode, a local two-player mode, and an online two-player mode when it was released on July 15, 1999, but the online network was discontinued on January 31, 2001.